Commonwealth heads of government to meet in Rwanda

   The next Commonwealth Heads of Government Meeting (CHOGM) has been
   officially launched in a video message from the President of Rwanda and
   the Commonwealth Secretary-General.

Secretary-General

   The Rt Hon Patricia Scotland QC is the sixth Commonwealth
   Secretary-General. She is the second Secretary-General from the
   Caribbean and the first woman to hold the post.
